#: ../../08-append.rst:203
msgid "北大中文《人民日报》199801-199806数据集介绍"
msgstr ""
"Introduction to the Peking University Chinese \"People's Daily\" "
"199801-199806 Dataset"

#: ../../08-append.rst:205
msgid "数据集概述"
msgstr "Dataset Overview"

#: ../../08-append.rst:207
msgid ""
"PFR语料库是在得到相关新闻信息中心许可的条件下，以1998年人民日报语料为对象制作的标注语料库。 "
"该数据集包含了1998年1月至6月的《人民日报》语料，旨在促进中文信息处理研究的发展。"
msgstr ""
"The PFR corpus is an annotated corpus produced based on the 1998 People's"
" Daily corpus with permission from the relevant news information center. "
"The dataset includes the \"People's Daily\" corpus from January to June "
"1998, aimed at promoting the development of Chinese information "
"processing research."

#: ../../08-append.rst:210
msgid "使用说明"
msgstr "Instructions for Use"

#: ../../08-append.rst:212
msgid "数据集获取：自4月3日起，PFR语料库1月份的语料在本仓库免费公开，用户可进行下载。"
msgstr ""
"Dataset Acquisition: Starting from April 3rd, the January corpus of the "
"PFR corpus is publicly available for free in this repository for users to"
" download."

#: ../../08-append.rst:213
msgid "制作规范：PFR语料库的制作遵循《现代汉语语料库加工——词语切分与词性标注规范》。"
msgstr ""
"Production Specification: The production of the PFR corpus follows the "
"\"Modern Chinese Corpus Processing—Word Segmentation and Part-of-Speech "
"Tagging Specifications\"."

#: ../../08-append.rst:214
msgid "引用说明：在使用或引用PFR语料库的研究或论文工作中，请务必注明来源。"
msgstr ""
"Citation Note: In research or papers using or citing the PFR corpus, "
"please be sure to indicate the source."

#: ../../08-append.rst:216
msgid "注意事项"
msgstr "Precautions"

#: ../../08-append.rst:218
msgid "请确保在研究和引用过程中遵循学术规范和道德准则。"
msgstr ""
"Please ensure academic standards and ethical guidelines are followed "
"during research and citation."

#: ../../08-append.rst:219
msgid "本数据集仅用于学术研究目的，不得用于任何商业用途。"
msgstr ""
"This dataset is for academic research purposes only and may not be used "
"for any commercial purposes."

#: ../../08-append.rst:220
msgid "我们希望这个数据集能为您的学术研究提供有益的帮助。"
msgstr "We hope this dataset will be helpful to your academic research."

